text: Atapattu Mudiyanselage Chamari Jayangani is a cricketer and the captain of the women's Twenty20 International team of Sri Lanka. Atapattu was born on February 9, 1990.Chamari Athapaththu == References == == Other websites == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers
